 比人鞭屍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T14:25:20.000Z","msg":"中哂point<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6535d72b3ee7f2af00637eaa6a0d10d140f2dc1a","tid":1024264,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T14:46:17.000Z","msg":"可否重設黑店/白店投票?"},{"pid":"3fe6098e05b31e99194ab9caa6654a33498c93c0","tid":1024264,"uid":77771,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T14:55:30.000Z","msg":"3C1J 已經算最穩陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673411ee09e3a6766b9c5384c8e8a499f2f3db62","tid":1024264,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3fe6098e05b31e99194ab9caa6654a33498c93c0","tid":1024264,"uid":77771,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T14:55:30.000Z","msg":"3C1J 已經算最穩陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T15:05:28.000Z","msg":"已經驚到走左去SE個D細鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167dadf27acd3a2808b60f253db24c6cf087e42a","tid":1024264,"uid":158480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"673411ee09e3a6766b9c5384c8e8a499f2f3db62","tid":1024264,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3fe6098e05b31e99194ab9caa6654a33498c93c0","tid":1024264,"uid":77771,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T14:55:30.000Z","msg":"3C1J 已經算最穩陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T15:05:28.000Z","msg":"已經驚到走左去SE個D細鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T18:07:13.000Z","msg":"Se 細鋪拎唔到咁多貨，有d貨可能都係3c賣比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc6d84d947f6c10c0b37facf632a763185630b1","t